Students are advised to consult with their respective teachers/professors. 

Be informed, ITHM Tamaraws!

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo
